{"tid":916801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墮馬頭落地暫癱瘓！安國倫頸椎骨折入ICU做手術","createTime":"2018-11-26T03:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T15:04:10.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"803c6c69b56a91eb294749c2d290214756367e0b","tid":916801,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543199860_901a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543199860_901a.jpg&h=4b42c4d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日（25日）墮馬受傷的澳洲籍騎師安國倫，據了解傷勢嚴重。他墮馬時由於頭部著地，頸椎骨折引致下半身未能郁動，一直於深切治療部留醫。<br />\n經醫生連夜進行檢查及掃描，認為傷勢嚴重，並已安排於今早九時半進行手術。安國倫的太太Erin已於凌晨抵港，隨即趕到威爾斯親王醫院陪伴丈夫。<br />\n安國倫昨日應馬會邀請來港策騎一日，並於較早場次策騎冠軍練馬師蔡約翰訓練的「請跟我來」勝出頭馬。正當以為會以好成績結束此行之際，到第九場卻遭逢不幸，其坐騎「美麗寶寶」出閘時向前一跪，安國倫隨即被摔下，頭部首先著地，伏在地上動彈不得，立即被送往醫院檢查。據了解初部發現頸椎骨折，需於今早（26日）接受手術。<br />\n冠軍騎師潘頓及太太Nicole與安國倫一家交情極深，當安國倫出事後，Nicole馬上通知身在澳洲的安國倫太太Erin，即時趕搭夜機來港。而潘頓昨賽後立即到醫院守候，直到凌晨一時才離開。至於Nicole更於凌晨四時親自到機場接機，並送Erin到威爾斯親王醫院探望丈夫。"},{"pid":"8f6f388ea5a56929f337ee0dde1cf8ee90828c38","tid":916801,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:27:53.000Z","msg":"馬rip"},{"pid":"61d0ac07910ca980c9a274616e199cac10fd33c9","tid":916801,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f66a88c08c38fc88ef91ed652a13ef1ad24c18","tid":916801,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f20de87e51870d2af390b02c65f64f6e045b95","tid":916801,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"隻馬仲慘，啪埋冇人提。"},{"pid":"164062651ffbaa3efe56aba2021074fba7848868","tid":916801,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望無事"},{"pid":"1845820dd5cafba046ff22c5908adf84cdee0b4d","tid":916801,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:57:38.000Z","msg":"美麗寶寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b31ca5af96ebd59469ae1a95b5bb68c231e1fd4","tid":916801,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報應"},{"pid":"e08b10bf6b1299a738d11b7135f849301a041075","tid":916801,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"係隻馬特登發脾氣，玩個騎師？"},{"pid":"4b78603476017c93d6e55808d3dea54abc9d6e04","tid":916801,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:47:09.000Z","msg":"人地雷神走得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb37a8dd2b17e8ab3bad1bbd8e57368ed43064f0","tid":916801,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca4ab755451431ccd1b19b6e780a1e7acb674f33","tid":916801,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"我見到上面好多個冚家剷"},{"pid":"afc177ab46d94e944b5cbd5ac27d94538af8a017","tid":916801,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca4ab755451431ccd1b19b6e780a1e7acb674f33","tid":916801,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"我見到上面好多個冚家剷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"原來兩個啫"},{"pid":"893639c7e04e2d3bfafdfb07289b93f632812733","tid":916801,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1845820dd5cafba046ff22c5908adf84cdee0b4d","tid":916801,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:57:38.00